@node intro "Introduction"
Introduction :
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
When I saw @{"Klondike" link reko} for the first time I was surprised of his nice graphics
and only when I saw Klondike II I thought about his 'standard' FORMAT.
The idea is to permit to create easy a new cardset and to use in more
than one game. I hope in future other Amiga programmers will use the @{"REKO" link rekoformat} format
in their card games.
@endnode

@node execution "Execution"
Execution :
~~~~~~~~~~~
Runs from Cli or workbench. Simply and easy.

@endnode

@node install "Installation"
Installation :
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
This is the easy part ...
Installing RekoMan isn't very tough ; you just need to copy it somewhere

To work need @{"ReqTools" link reqtools}

@endnode

